# Results

## Overall Performance by Phase and Group

```{r overall-table}
overall <- by_grp |>
  mutate(
    Accuracy        = fmt_pct(accuracy),
    `RT correct`    = fmt_rt(rt_correct),
    `RT incorrect`  = fmt_rt(rt_incorrect),
    `RT all`        = fmt_rt(rt_all),
    Phase           = stringr::str_to_title(as.character(phase))
  ) |>
  select(Group = group, Phase, Accuracy,
         `RT correct`, `RT incorrect`, `RT all`,
